Market Segmentation: 
The heat pump market is segmented on the basis of type, energy source, category, capacity, power and sector. The growth amongst the different segments helps you in attaining the knowledge related to the different growth factors expected to be prevalent throughout the market and formulate different strategies to help identify core application areas and the difference in your target market.
On the basis of type, the market is segmented into ducted and ductless.
On the basis of energy source, the market is segmented into air/water, air/air, ground/geothermal source and hybrid.
On the basis of category, the market is segmented into reversible air-air w/heating, h- air/water h-ground/water, sanitary hot water, reversible others and exhaust air.
On the basis of capacity, the market is segmented into units < 20KW and units > 20 KW.
On the basis of power, the market is segmented into electric and gas driven.
On the basis of sector, the market is segmented into residential, commercial and industrial.
